            <h5 class="card-title">Grounded by weak biz, IT companies cut travel bills by half</h5>
            <p class="card-text">Top IT service providers in India have cut their travel costs by almost half since the
              Covid-19 pandemic due to weak demand and strict US visa policies. For IT companies, travel expenses
              largely include on-site travel for sales meetings, CXO meetings, including accommodation, transportation
              and visa costs.</p>
